# ATL (AT Command Library) for SIMCom Modems

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-Proprietary-blue.svg)](https://github.com/yourusername/atl-library/blob/main/LICENSE)
[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-1.0.0-green.svg)](https://github.com/yourusername/atl-library)
[![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Embedded-lightgrey.svg)](https://github.com/yourusername/atl-library)

A powerful, asynchronous AT command processing library for SIMCom modems, designed for embedded systems with minimal resource consumption.

